        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1661885923" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer749015905749740424">This was a very enjoyable book to read, although it was a little confusing at times. It follows many interconnected characters spread over many decades, all linked by a beech tree. The writing is good and solid, the characters are rich and interesting, and the plot is engaging. As a bonus, many of the events are set in West Michigan areas that I&apos;m familiar with.</span>
  <span id="freeText749015905749740424" style="display:none">This was a very enjoyable book to read, although it was a little confusing at times. It follows many interconnected characters spread over many decades, all linked by a beech tree. The writing is good and solid, the characters are rich and interesting, and the plot is engaging. As a bonus, many of the events are set in West Michigan areas that I'm familiar with.</span>
