<span id="freeTextContainer10168802243145961232">A book about sweet, sad and touching stories. It hurt me to read some things and made me laugh out loud so it was successful in pulling heart strings. However it was a little confusing and I guess if you read it straight without trying to link the stories it would be better. I spent the first half of the book trying to figure what was what until I gave up and just read it for what it was... a good story.</span>

          </span>
